# Fixture images live in a fixture object store (S3, not git); CI syncs them here and
# devs copy them here manually for local runs (see fixture/README.md). Track only the
# README so the folder + instructions exist in git; never the image bytes.
fixture/*
!fixture/README.md
# several-sources CLI build artifacts (built at CI time by build-cli-sources.js).
cli-builds/
cli-sources-resolved.json
# candidate/baseline addon prebuilds staged by CI (A2); swapped into ./prebuilds.
builds/
# misc
node_modules/
*.tgz
# Dima's internal reference (kept local, not committed per request)
VLM_General_Benchmark.md
